 them first\, and then finding out how they  imagine they can support the Ap
 ril 18th Town hall - 10 minutes <br></li><li>NG - What programming we shoul
 d do together before (in part to ensure a successful vote in June)? - Break
 out 15 minutes - Check back in with the big group - 5 minuets </li><li>DH -
  Next steps- Should we make this (the Summit) a regular event? or what shou
 ld we do to support these inititiatives- 5 minutes</li><li>Wrap up - Proces
 s Observation - Action Item review - 5 minutes </li><li>Closing - 5 minutes
