UID:5h56c3uu6cfkel8rleqrv5iv7r_R20210314T153000@google.com
CREATED:20210112T155501Z
DESCRIPTION:<br>Bibleodeon introduces our youth to Hebrew and Christian scr
 iptures by presenting the best-known stories from these traditions with eng
 aging and interactive lesson. The goals are for the children to become fami
 liar with a range of well-known Bible stories\, know how to find their way 
 around the Bible\, and have a basic understanding of the Bible’s history an
 d power. This year we will add a twist to this class by structuring the sto
 ries so that there will be a review of what the kids learn done in a Minecr
 aft format with those who have the game helping to imagine the Bible story 
 in a Minecraft environment.<br><a href="https://onrealm.org/uumontclair/Pub
 licRegistrations/Event?linkString=MTEyYThjNzgtMjFmZC00YzY1LTliMzYtYWMwMDAxN
 zAwMjdi">REGISTER HERE</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20210310T002856Z
LOCATION:Zoom Video Conference 
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:4th/5th Grade RE Class
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
