 ion and the wider community to develop\, strengthen and act upon anti-racis
 t\, multicultural perspectives through worship services\, educational progr
 ams\, lectures\, book &amp\; film discussions\, other cultural events\, and
  community involvement.</p><p><a href="https://www.uumontclair.org/ministri
 es/urt/">For more information click here.&nbsp\;</a></p>
