DESCRIPTION:<html-blob><p>Sacred Wheel CUUPs will be holding an Open Healin
 g Circle on&nbsp\;Sunday Feb 20 at 7:30 p.m.&nbsp\;&nbsp\;via Zoom.</p><p>F
 or those unfamiliar -healing circles are similar to prayers. Healing could 
 be for physical\, emotional or spiritual. It is the intent we put into it. 
 If you would like to assist or have a request for yourself or someone else\
 , please join us. If you like to join in and have no experience\, we will t
 each you. Alternatively\, if you are new to this\, you can just sit back an
 d observe. Stick around afterwards for a sharing of ghost stories.&nbsp\;</
 p><p>All are welcome to Sacred Wheel CUUPs events. For more information\, <
 a href="mailto:sacredwheelcuups@uumontclair.org" id="ow1005" __is_owner="tr
 ue">contact Ann Trip</a> or visit us on <a href="http://facebook.com/groups
 /UUCMSacredWheel" id="ow1022" __is_owner="true">Facebook</a>.<br></p></html
 -blob>
LAST-MODIFIED:20220127T171544Z
LOCATION:Zoom Video Conference
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Healing Circle
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
