CREATED:20210112T155538Z
DESCRIPTION:These classes will be outdoor in-person meetings for 8th Grade 
 OWL. We are not able to conduct OWL classes via Zoom. Although\, meeting ou
 tdoors with masks is not ideal\, with some modifications\, we feel we can c
 over most of the OWL curriculum. Unlike many other sexuality curricula curr
 ently available\, this program is comprehensive and progressive. In an incl
 usive and developmentally appropriate manner\, it addresses sensitive topic
 s that are typically excluded in other Sex Ed curricula. We plan to start m
 eeting in March\, but we will not be able to finish the curriculum by the e
 nd of June\, so we will resume in September and finish up in October. Comin
 g of Age will begin after OWL is wrapped up. Some details still need to be 
 figured out\, but we expect to be able to lead OWL workshops with some smal
 l modifications to the curriculum to accommodate safety measures.<br><br><a
  href="mailto:owl@uumontclair.org" id="ow6849" __is_owner="true">Contact fo
 r more information</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20210310T003154Z
LOCATION:Socially Distant Outdoors
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:8th Grade RE Class
TRANSP:OPAQUE
