CREATED:20170823T191802Z
DESCRIPTION:UUCM Middle School Youth are welcomed to register for the UUA J
 r.\nYouth Autumn Retreat September 9-10\, 2017. This retreat is for all UUC
 M\nyouth who will be in 6th\, 7th or 8th grade in autumn 2017. Twice a year
 \,\nthe UUA hosts a 24 hour retreat or CON that is filled with other UU you
 th\,\ngames\, music and more. It is at Camp Herlich located in Patterson\, 
 NY. We\nwill leave Saturday\, Sept 9 and return Sunday morning Sept 10 and 
 in\nbetween make memories and have a lot of fun. Pre-registration is requir
 ed through the UUA at\nhttp://www.uua.org/central-east/events/youth/ny-patt
 erson-jr-youth-retreat?month=2017-09. For info\, contact UUCM parent Jill W
 odnick (jillwodnick@gmail.com) who is happy to answer questions about previ
 ous junior youth UUA CONS and is registered as one of the chaperones for ou
 r congregation.
LAST-MODIFIED:20170905T135304Z
LOCATION:Patterson\, NY 12563\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:UUA Junior Youth Autumn Retreat 
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
