 /Event?linkString=MDBjZWFmMmUtYWVlOC00MjNjLTk5MDQtYWQzYzAxODRmNmE3" id="ow1
 778" __is_owner="true">REGISTER HERE</a></p><p><br></p><p>Our 2021 Inter-Co
 ngregational Summer Adventure</p><p>6 Weeks\, 6&nbsp\;Unitarian Universalis
 t Sources</p><p>will run from July 16th thru August 20th from 4:00pm to 5:0
 0PM (Eastern).</p><p><br></p><p>Upcoming Grades 6th&nbsp\;through 8th</p><p
 ><br></p><p><strong>MISSION STATEMENT:</strong></p><p><strong>Our mission i
 s to sustain a network of faith support for UU children\, youth and familie
 s everywhere. As an inter-congregational collective\, we’re working to stre
 ngthen our denomination by using the virtual space to transcend church wall
 s\, widen reach and nurture grounds for connection through a system of shar
 ed values.</strong><br></p><p><br></p><p>This program is absolutely flexibl
 e.&nbsp\; We look forward to having all&nbsp\;attend on Fridays through Aug
 ust 20th when they can.</p><p><br></p>
