DTSTAMP:20260311T022957Z
UID:4ofg1hoc8ptj22f8cege6ks119_R20210319T170000@google.com
CREATED:20201117T221352Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Co led by Claudia Sanders\, Judie Rinerson and Rev. Anya Sam
 mler-Michael\, our journey together will traverse the stories and experienc
 es of elders\, offering insights into navigating this unique stage of life.
  Our core text\, "In Later Years: Finding Meaning and Spirit in Aging" by U
 nitarian Universalist minister\, Rev. Bruce Marshall\, draws on scores of p
 ersonal interviews\, and provides a felt sense\, grounded in real-life acco
 unts\, of the challenges and blessings of aging. Unlike many books on the t
 opic\, In Later Years: Finding Meaning and Spirit in Aging focuses particul
 arly on older seniors—those in their late seventies\, eighties\, and nineti
 es. The book also serves as an invaluable resource for family members and c
 aregivers\, suggesting ways to help\, ways to connect\, and ways to underst
 and the issues that attend growing old.&nbsp\;</p><p><a href="https://onrea
 lm.org/uumontclair/PublicRegistrations/Event?linkString=OTViOWNkZjQtYWY5MC0
 0YWYxLWE4MmMtYWM3NjAxNzBkYWZj" id="ow8711" __is_owner="true">REGISTER HERE<
 /a></p><p>Every participant will want their own copy of the<a href="https:/
 /www.amazon.com/Later-Years-Finding-Meaning-Spirit-ebook/dp/B07B9WGX9S">&nb
 sp\;book.</a>&nbsp\;<br></p><p>We will begin over Zoom\, and may move to in
 -person as we are able. Participants are encouraged to read the first two c
 hapters before we meet on January 15th.&nbsp\;</p><p><br></p><p>Fridays 1-2
 :30pm</p><p>Dates:&nbsp\;</p><p>January 15<br>Feb 19<br>March 19<br>April 1
 6<br>May 21<br>June 18&nbsp\;</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20210316T213908Z
LOCATION:Zoom Video Conference
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:In Later Years - Finding Meaning and Spirit in Aging
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
