 ummit 2022</b><br>Tuesday April 26th 7-9:30pm<br>In-person in our Peierls R
 oom and Virtual<br><br>We are moving through unprecedented&nbsp\;times as a
  congregation. Let's continue to move through them\, together. At our Leade
 r's Summit we will:&nbsp\;<br>• Work together to achieve our&nbsp\;mission\
 , vision\, and strategic&nbsp\;plan.•&nbsp\;Set a visional focus for the&nb
 sp\;coming&nbsp\;congregational year.<br>•&nbsp\;Break down silos through c
 ollaboration across program and ministry areas.<br>•&nbsp\;Plan ahead&nbsp\
 ;to increase&nbsp\;opportunities\,&nbsp\;outrea<wbr>ch and in-<br>reach.<br
 >•&nbsp\;Serve leaders with key information and the means for support<br><b
 r>One to three leaders from your team\, council\, program or committee are 
 encouraged to attend. Small group and Covenant group leaders are also welco
 me. Our time together will include space for connection\, sharing\, deepeni
 ng\, and learning.&nbsp\;
