UID:46cbinec0jir8mif99403ms12o@google.com
CREATED:20210428T205003Z
DESCRIPTION:This exciting one-hour event features:&nbsp\;<br><ul><li>Chris 
 Durkin\, the Essex County Clerk\,&nbsp\;</li><li>Dr. Marcheta P. Evans\, th
 e President of Bloomfield College (the first woman and the first Black pers
 on to hold that position)\,&nbsp\;</li><li>Darryl Jeffries\, the President 
 of the NAACP of the Oranges and Maplewood\, and&nbsp\;</li><li>The Choir fr
 om Arts High School in Newark\, the premier performing arts high school in 
 the state.&nbsp\;&nbsp\;</li></ul><br><br>This is going to be one-hour pack
 ed with solid information about the changes in voter registration and the r
 egulations that have been put in place post the November 2020 election\; pe
 p talks on the importance of voting in local and statewide elections\; and\
 , a performance by the choir of one of the region's best performing arts hi
 gh schools\, Arts High School -- Newark.<br><br>Clearly\, this is an event 
 not to be missed.&nbsp\; It is especially important for newly registered vo
 ters.&nbsp\;&nbsp\;<b>If you have a high-school senior or an 18-year</b>-<b
 >old\, encourage them to sign on.</b><br><br><a href="https://us02web.zoom.
 us/meeting/register/tZckce6srzotE9J4Np3JCz8IJUOi3xWdCL4X" id="ow1081" __is_
 owner="true">REGISTER HERE </a>and sign on for this not-to-be-missed civic 
 affair.
LAST-MODIFIED:20210428T205003Z
LOCATION:Zoom Video Conference
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Voting in 2021...It's not what you think it is! -- with the League 
 of Women Voters of the Montclair Area
TRANSP:OPAQUE
ATTACH;FILENAME=final PDF-May 6-Chris Durkin speaker.pptx-1.pdf;FMTTYPE=app
 lication/pdf:https://drive.google.com/file/d/1vExl8KJqYL9LlZ2lCkP0k1Z2oJWQ6
 4MU/view?usp=drive_web
