CREATED:20210227T003408Z
DESCRIPTION:Please join with our UUCM community as we share together in our
  Zoom Passover Seder\, which will be held on March 29 (the 3rd night of Pas
 sover\, 2021) at 6 pm.<br><br>You can prepare your own Seder plate and enjo
 y the ceremonial foods as we read together\, along with wine/grape juice an
 d matzo\, or you can follow along and watch. No need to have a fancy Seder 
 plate either - you can even create one on paper. The bottom photo is of a s
 eder plate created by my granddaughter years ago\, and is treasured.<br><br
 ><a href="https://www.myjewishlearning.com/article/the-seder-plate/">https:
 //www.myjewishlearning.com/article/the-seder-plate/</a><br><br><a href="htt
 ps://onrealm.org/uumontclair/PublicRegistrations/Event?linkString=ZGRiMDYwN
 mUtN2Q3OC00YzIwLWI3ZTgtYWNkYzAwMDc0MTc0" id="ow13025" __is_owner="true">Reg
 ister Here</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20210316T215011Z
LOCATION:Zoom Video Conference
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Passover Seder
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
