DESCRIPTION:<p>2021 Spring&nbsp\;"People's Choice"&nbsp\;Bible Study - Wher
 e We Will Examine what YOU want to Study - Thursdays - May 6\, May 13\, May
  20 &amp\; 27 - 7-830pm on Zoom.</p><p><br></p><p>Come encounter the Judeo 
 Christian Scriptures through a Unitarian Universalist lens. Rev Scott will 
 lead an examination of texts suggested by the class. A good Study Bible wil
 l help best prepare you for this class ~ and it's a good thing to add to yo
 ur library! The NRSV or NIV are two translations we recommend.&nbsp\;</p><p
 ><a href="https://onrealm.org/uumontclair/PublicRegistrations/Event?linkStr
 ing=NWQ4N2U5NTEtNWEzMS00YTk5LTg2ODYtYWNmYjAxM2I3NTc3" id="ow1004" __is_owne
 r="true">Registration is $10 per person. Register now here.</a></p><p>After
  you register\, send Rev Scott&nbsp\;the Bible Passages/Stories&nbsp\;you w
 ant us to explore.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>
