UID:3eb6uvbv283ah3ghh3r48q83cn@google.com
CREATED:20211027T140506Z
DESCRIPTION:<h1>Help Needed in the Archives!</h1><p>If you were involved wi
 th the Congregation in any way in the 50’s\, 60’s or 70’s\, please let us k
 now!&nbsp\; We have found some slides and undated pictures that show people
  from those times\, and we have no idea who some of the people are.&nbsp\; 
 We need you to help us with that if you can.&nbsp\;&nbsp\;We also need your
  knowledge to tell us your stories of what was happening at UUCM.&nbsp\; Wh
 at were your memories of Religious Education\, Social Justice\, social even
 ts\, and culture in those times?&nbsp\; How do the worship services compare
  to those of today?&nbsp\; Do you remember the Collegiate Pulpit and Unity 
 Speakers?&nbsp\; What was the music and art like?&nbsp\;&nbsp\;The Archivis
 ts are planning a multi-platform meeting on November 17\, 2021 with former 
 UUCM ministers Rev. Charlie Ortman and Rev. Lee Barker joining us virtually
 . We will show you some of these pictures.&nbsp\; You may be aware we are b
 eginning to put our archival information online. If you would like to help 
 us with this project please plan to participate in this meeting. We would b
 e grateful for your help. Please email&nbsp\;<a href="mailto:archives@umont
 clair.org">archives@umontclair.org</a>.&nbsp\; We look forward to talking w
 ith you.&nbsp\;Your help is vital to our project!&nbsp\; &nbsp\;</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20211028T230412Z
LOCATION:Zoom Video Conference\, UUCM-1-Peierls (60)
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:UUMontclair Archives Presentation
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
