 ad you have found your way here! Join us for our Pathways to Membership cla
 ss! Now is the time to consider deepening your understanding of the Unitari
 an Universalist tradition and our congregational life. This class is your p
 ath to becoming a member of Unitarian Universalist Congregation at Montclai
 r. Bring your questions and your hopes. Building community takes intention.
  This is one important step on that intentional path.\n\nRegister Today!
LAST-MODIFIED:20211026T142025Z
