DESCRIPTION:<html-blob><u></u>You are invited to join us for our virtual Co
 nnection Café every Sunday at 4 PM via Zoom. If you haven’t yet experienced
  our online Connection Café\, give it a try. Participants report that this 
 format allows us to build relationships across the congregation in ways tha
 t will sustain us as individual participants and support our growth as a co
 mmunity. So join us for a fun way to connect on Sunday afternoon. All are w
 elcome. We hope you can join us!&nbsp\;<br><br><a href="https://tinyurl.com
 /UUCMCafe" id="ow3176" __is_owner="true">CLICK HERE TO JOIN NOW</a><br>Phon
 e # +1 929 205 6099/ ID: 984 9553 9203<u></u></html-blob>
