 " __is_owner="true">CLICK HERE TO REGISTER</a><br><br><p>Our Candlelight Se
 rvice is evocative\, rich with depth and reflection\, and features the asto
 unding gift of a multi-part orchestra and thirty person choir.</p><p>Join U
