CREATED:20210315T211123Z
DESCRIPTION:Join Rev Scott and Director of Religious Education (DRE) Judith
  Hogan Saturday\, April 10\, 1 - 3:30pm for a "Start-Up" Workshop. We will 
 more deeply investigate how to work together\, examine systemic issues in R
 E here at UUCM\, explore UUCM's unique RE vision and identity\, and set exp
 ectations for our DRE\, now well into her first year. We need your input as
  we work to plan for a fruitful and meaningful time together. RE TEAM\, Boa
 rd\, Teachers\, Past RE Leaders and other interested parties are invited to
  attend.<br><br>Registration is FREE! <br><a href="https://onrealm.org/uumo
 ntclair/PublicRegistrations/Event?linkString=YTk2Yzg5MDItNzg3Mi00MTUyLTgyNj
 ItYWNlZDAwZmExNmZi" id="ow4162" __is_owner="true">Register Here</a>
