CREATED:20200804T183858Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>It is open to all members and friends of UUCM who have Jewis
 h roots or relatives and/or an interest in learning more about Jewish custo
 ms and culture.&nbsp\;</p><p><br></p><p>The group will provide an opportuni
 ty to honor Jewish heritage\, share cultural and religious memories\, and e
 xplore feelings about dual identity as UU and Jewish. Much of the focus wil
 l be shaped&nbsp\;by the interests and needs of attendees.&nbsp\;</p><p><br
 ></p><p>We’ll meet on Zoom at 7:30. Let us know you’re interested and we’ll
  send you a link shortly before the start of the meeting.&nbsp\;</p><p><br>
 </p><p>Hope to see you!</p><p><b></b><br></p><p><b>Hilary Fandel\, Marcia M
 andel\, and Helen Lippman&nbsp\;</b></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20200804T183858Z
LOCATION:via zoom
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:UUs for Jewish Awareness
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
