DTEND:20211109T013000Z
DTSTAMP:20260311T022957Z
UID:702qvlca1q1pq2p6amslfckakn@google.com
CREATED:20211025T152553Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Sacred Wheel CUUPs will be holding an Open Healing Circle an
 d a&nbsp\;virtual campfire with a&nbsp\;telling of Ghost stories on Monday\
 , November 8\, 2021 at 7:30 p.m. via Zoom.</p><p>If you would like to assis
 t or have a request for yourself or someone else\, please join us. For thos
 e unfamiliar -healing circles are similar to prayers. It is the intent we p
 ut into it. If you like to join in and have no experience\, we will teach y
 ou. Healing could be for physical\, emotional or spiritual. Alternatively\,
  if you are new to this\, you can just sit back and observe. Stick around a
 fterwards for a sharing of ghost stories. All are welcome. <a href="mailto:
 sacredwheelcuups@uumontclair.org" id="ow713" __is_owner="true">For more inf
 ormation email Ann.&nbsp\;</a></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20211025T152553Z
LOCATION:Zoom Video Conference
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Sacred Wheel CUUPs Open Healing Circle
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
