DESCRIPTION:The holiday season is sometimes very challenging even without a
  pandemic. UUCM Sacred Wheel CUUPs is offering a grounding and centering wo
 rkshop to teach you how to stay grounded. Grounding is a way of eliminating
  excess energy or negativity. Learn simple but valuable grounding and cente
 ring tools to help you get through these uncertain times. Join us to learn 
 these important techniques to keep balanced through the rest of 2021.&nbsp\
 ; <a href="mailto:sacredwheelcuups@uumontclair.org">For more information em
 ail Ann.&nbsp\;</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20211025T152814Z
