DESCRIPTION:The New Member Covenant Group is a group for new members and vi
 sitors looking to deepen in their connection to our congregation. The group
  meets for six sessions\, on days and times determined by the participants 
 availability. New groups begin every October and every January. Co-led by t
 wo recent new members and Rev. Anya these groups help participants develop 
 in their relationship to one another as well as our congregation.<br><a hre
 f="mailto:revanya@uumontclair.org" id="ow13529" __is_owner="true">For more 
 information contact Rev. Anya</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20210408T183436Z
