 llaboration with Montclair Mutual Aid our congregation has erected a perman
 ent space to provide food and other necessary provisions to our local commu
 nity. The pantry will be filled first by our senior youth group. Join in th
 is celebration of community care and youth empowerment. 1pm on our congrega
 tion's grounds: 67 Church Street\, Montclair\, NJ. 
