DESCRIPTION:<p>Our Annual Meeting will be held&nbsp\;Sunday\,&nbsp\;<strong
 >JUNE 6\, 2021</strong>\, at 11 AM via Zoom.&nbsp\;</p><p>At this meeting\,
  as in years past\, you will be able to hear reports from the president and
  your ministers about the state of the congregation\, you will hear from th
 e Social Justice Coalition about its plans for the coming year\, and import
 antly\, you will be able to vote on important issues including a proposed b
 ylaws change\, a slate of candidates for leadership positions in the congre
 gation\, and our proposed budget for the next year.&nbsp\;</p><p><br></p><p
 ><a href="https://onrealm.org/uumontclair/PublicRegistrations/Event?linkStr
 ing=ZDdmOTFlOGUtMjllMy00MTE2LTgwOTUtYWQyNjAxODA5YTc2" id="ow550" __is_owner
 ="true">CLICK HERE TO REGISTER</a></p>
