UID:5ga7rg6q3hg6j1ua11bhh2sh3t@google.com
CREATED:20210811T184403Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Mark your calendar—Our 2021 UU FaithAction NJ&nbsp\;<b>Fall 
 Issues Conference</b>&nbsp\;will be&nbsp\;<strong>October 16th.</strong>&nb
 sp\;The Issues Conference&nbsp\;is your opportunity to help decide the just
 ice issues New Jersey&nbsp\;Unitarian Universalists focus on for&nbsp\;2021
 -2022!<br></p><p>We are excited to announce our&nbsp\;<strong>Keynote Speak
 er&nbsp\;</strong>will be&nbsp\;Senate Majority Leader&nbsp\;<strong><a hre
 f="https://default.salsalabs.org/T9c8fb83d-16a2-4ea6-b5dc-9cfd15545640/7d16
 377d-59af-43ce-9b27-7530582ad6bb">Loretta Weinberg</a>.</strong>&nbsp\;Over
  her&nbsp\;career\, Sen. Weinberg has championed matters of conscience incl
 uding&nbsp\;criminal justice reform\, gun violence prevention\,&nbsp\;marri
 age equality\, gender equality&nbsp\;and reproductive justice. Having annou
 nced&nbsp\;<a href="https://default.salsalabs.org/Ta8bc554b-a7c9-4c9b-bb9e-
 8d26c7ab27ef/7d16377d-59af-43ce-9b27-7530582ad6bb">plans for&nbsp\;retireme
 nt</a>&nbsp\;in January\, she hopes her legacy will be&nbsp\;“a whole gener
 ation of troublemakers” following her into politics.</p><p>Our 2021 Fall Is
 sues Conference will be hosted by&nbsp\;<strong>Morristown Unitarian Univer
 salist Fellowship</strong>&nbsp\;and their stellar tech team. Due to the&nb
 sp\;uncertain development of public health conditions\, we will be making a
  final determination mid-September as to whether our 2021 Issues Conference
  will convene in a&nbsp\;<strong>hybrid</strong>&nbsp\;(options to attend a
 t Morristown OR on Zoom) or&nbsp\;<strong>virtual</strong>&nbsp\;(Zoom only
 ) format. A finalized schedule and registration will be forthcoming.</p><p>
 Save the date\, and invite your friends!&nbsp\;We hope to see you there.<br
 ></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20210811T184403Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Fall Issues Conference - Faith Action
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
