DESCRIPTION:Concerns or Questions about Religious Education?\n\nWe are hold
 ing a listening circle for those who may have had an unfortunate experience
  with our religious education program over the past couple of years. This l
 istening circle will be similar to the ones we held after our Interim Minis
 ter experience - designed for you to be fully heard\, for us to learn from 
 any systemic issues that may need to be addressed\, and for us to move forw
 ard as a congregation. \nJoin us on Zoom on Saturday March 27th at 1:00 pm.
  If you can’t make this date please reach out directly to Rev. Scott Sammle
 r-Michael via email at revscott@uumontclair.org\nIn faith and accountabilit
 y\,\nGhana Hylton & Jason Brome on behalf of the UUCM RE Team
