DESCRIPTION:<br>Memorial Service for Jordan T. Tassy -&nbsp\;<br>April 10th
 \, 11:30am at Nishuane Park<br>&amp\; Live Streamed over Facebook&nbsp\;<br
 ><br>Norma Tassy invites family\, friends\, and community members with a co
 nnection to her son to honor and celebrate Jordan Tassy’s life.&nbsp\;<br><
 br>You are invited to bring a flower to the Memorial. Individual flowers wi
 ll be arranged in common vases\, symbolizing the incredible effect that Jor
 dan Tassy has had on all of our lives.&nbsp\;<br><br>Following the Memorial
  guests are invited to greet the family and gather for a repast at the home
  of Tanya Coke and George Kendall\, 110 High Street in Montclair.&nbsp\;<br
 ><br>If you will join the memorial in person at Nishuane park\, consider br
 inging your own chair. Chairs will not be provided. Hand sanitizer and mask
 s will be provided.&nbsp\;<br><br>If you wish to join virtually you will be
  able to find the memorial live streamed on our UUCM Facebook page:&nbsp\;<
 a href="http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001N5XUyVaLQLulSj7dhaZTKNkYtLLnfcH0R5Fv
 3Z6G2rY0GarEkTwDtMWjossKSufmrpuwEN9O11H6MLDuvL8-Gbw7YB8l5mVA32N1UwxTsjGzLrf
 0zqkQ9LwDJ0djf5b5aiDn9vAetX91srfdW3mO9zv203kDv5p4&amp\;c=2lCzKf-nixpwxRWS7N
 BI-AwBx8Mq5fsteKX40TkXg9JrRKVWE1oj0Q==&amp\;ch=YpnNuz0sIuixdT0O4BY-JmAcm4AQ
 Cl740pNcZ7bNiP0jBXBxK9IOXQ==">https://www.facebook.<wbr>com/uumontclair</a>
 <br>A Facebook event is being created that will provide you with a direct l
 ink. This information will be broadcast soon.&nbsp\;
LAST-MODIFIED:20210406T193654Z
LOCATION:Nishuane Park\, Montclair\, NJ 07042\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Memorial Service for Jordan Tassy
TRANSP:OPAQUE
