X-GOOGLE-CONFERENCE:https://meet.google.com/udn-yapz-ovy
CREATED:20220610T210730Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Join the Work Party (For Those With The Skill and/or The Wil
 l)! Announcing UUCM&#39\;s next SWeat Equity Team (SWET) Projects. UUCM&#39
 \;ers with will and skill are invited to assist in fixing things and spruci
 ng up our Building and Grounds. If you are good with some skills with tools
 \, or have the will to learn (and can follow directions)\, join Rev Scott a
 nd his team of SWET All-Stars. <br><br></p><p>Our 125 year old facility nee
 ds constant TLC. Come have fun with us and help provide the kind of hands-o
 n-ministry that builds community and a sense of ownership of our historic b
 uildings\, the &quot\;Mother Ship&quot\; of all we do. <br><br></p><p>All p
 rojects shall be approved by Aesthetics\, Building and Grounds and the Dire
 ctor of Facilities in advance. <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https:
 //onrealm.org/uumontclair/PublicRegistrations/Event?linkString%3DZTJlM2Q2NG
 UtOThiOS00MmZmLTkyMDMtYWViMDAxNWI4ZTBi&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;
 ust=1655327218701366&amp\;usg=AOvVaw0lOxrQE2bhXzT5yP2XZz37" target="_blank"
 ><u>Sign up by clicking here\, today! </u></a></p>\n\nJoin with Google Meet
 : https://meet.google.com/udn-yapz-ovy\nOr dial: (US) +1 260-218-1761 PIN: 
 436793826#\nMore phone numbers: https://tel.meet/udn-yapz-ovy?pin=481839694
 8006&hs=7\n\nLearn more about Meet at: https://support.google.com/a/users/a
 nswer/9282720
LAST-MODIFIED:20220612T101602Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:SWET TEAM Summer Fun 1
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
