DTSTART:20221008T170000Z
DTEND:20221008T180000Z
DTSTAMP:20260311T022957Z
UID:4tksrb1htri4g8gl5d279ltc2r@google.com
CREATED:20220725T150530Z
DESCRIPTION:We will gather with all ages and all species on the front lawn 
 of our Congregation<br><br><u><a href="https://onrealm.org/uumontclair/Publ
 icRegistrations/Event?linkString=ODFhMTc3NDUtZDQyNS00MjEzLWFjZWYtYWVkZDAwZj
 k5MWFi" id="ow7476" __is_owner="true">REGISTER HERE</a></u><br><br><br>With
  joy\, song and ritual we will bless our pets\, and our dear stuffed animal
 s.&nbsp\;<br><br>This service draws from the inspiration of St. Francis of 
 Assisi. In this Unitarian Universalist version we will take a moment to gri
 eve the animals that have died\, share our gratitude for the animals that m
 ake our lives better\, bless the animals that make their home among us\, an
 d commit to treating our animals like partners not things.<br><br>Please br
 ing donations of pet food\, treats\, used towels\, or monetary&nbsp\;contri
 butions to serve animals in local shelters.&nbsp\;
LAST-MODIFIED:20220725T150959Z
LOCATION:UUCM-1-Front Lawn (100)
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Animal Blessing
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
