X-GOOGLE-CONFERENCE:https://meet.google.com/jsh-kbne-npa
CREATED:20181003T222536Z
DESCRIPTION:Love and Connection Vespers Service \nFebruary 14th (Yup\, Vale
 ntines Day) \nBrought to you by the Ministers and the Care Team\n7:30-8:30p
 m\n\nAn evening vespers service that focuses on love and connection. Consid
 er this an alternative and spiritually inspiring way to spend an often chal
 lenging holiday. We will honor the grief that accompanies the loss of a lov
 ed one and we will celebrate the love connections that can literally save o
 ur lives. Come solo\, come with a loved one\, come with young ones. All are
  welcome. There will be singing\, candle lighting\, testimony\, meditation\
 , prayer\, and a chocolate communion!\n\nJoin with Google Meet: https://mee
 t.google.com/jsh-kbne-npa\nOr dial: (US) +1 407-986-7075 PIN: 829359377#\n\
 nLearn more about Meet at: https://support.google.com/a/users/answer/928272
 0
LAST-MODIFIED:20221206T042422Z
LOCATION:Sanctuary
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Love and Connection Vespers Service
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
