CREATED:20220127T162152Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><a href="https://onrealm.org/uumontclair/PublicRegistrations
 /Event?linkString=Y2RlZWQxNTctZjg2Mi00NTIzLWIwMDAtYWUzZTAxMGNlODI0" id="ow8
 13" __is_owner="true">REGISTER HERE</a></p><p><br></p><p>Our Passover Seder
  will be held on&nbsp\;Saturday April 16th&nbsp\;at 6:00 PM in Fletcher Hal
 l&nbsp\;(or perhaps outdoor\, if the weather permits).&nbsp\;Let’s get toge
 ther for an&nbsp\;evening to celebrate our&nbsp\;freedom and the hope of&nb
 sp\;emancipation of all people!<br></p><p><br></p><p>Food\, drink and a&nbs
 p\;wonderful Passover service will help us reflect together about our past 
 and &nbsp\;to think about our future. All are welcome! We need &nbsp\;speci
 fic food donations and assistance from all who&nbsp\;participate.<br></p><p
 ><br></p><p>The&nbsp\;requested donation&nbsp\;is $15 per adult (ages 13 &a
 mp\; up) &nbsp\;and $6 per child (ages 5 thru 12).<br></p><p><br></p><p><a 
 href="mailto:jewishawareness@uumontclair.org." id="ow826" __is_owner="true"
 >For more information please contact Hilary Fandel.</a></p>\n\nJoin with Go
 ogle Meet: https://meet.google.com/egt-czkt-xfo\nOr dial: (US) +1 470-273-8
 487 PIN: 416536963#\nMore phone numbers: https://tel.meet/egt-czkt-xfo?pin=
 6851965077226&hs=7\n\nLearn more about Meet at: https://support.google.com/
 a/users/answer/9282720
LAST-MODIFIED:20220415T184609Z
LOCATION:UUCM-1-Fletcher Hall (306)
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Passover Seder
TRANSP:OPAQUE
