DESCRIPTION:<html-blob>You are invited to join us for our virtual Connectio
 n Café every Sunday at 11:30 AM via Zoom and socially distant in person (no
  food or drink is provided but feel free to bring your own beverage). If yo
 u haven’t yet experienced our online Connection Café\, give it a try. Parti
 cipants report that this format allows us to build relationships across the
  congregation in ways that will sustain us as individual participants and s
 upport our growth as a community. So grab your coffee and join us for a fun
  way to connect on Sunday morning. All are welcome. We hope you can join us
 !&nbsp\;<br><br><br><a href="https://tinyurl.com/UUCMCafe">CLICK HERE TO JO
 IN NOW</a><br>Phone # +1 929 205 6099/ ID: 984 9553 9203<u></u><u></u></htm
 l-blob>
