CLASS:PUBLIC
CREATED:20190305T145616Z
DESCRIPTION:Spring Bible Study - A UU Lens on the End of Jesus' Life\n\nJoi
 n Rev Scott as we explore the sacred stories surrounding the end of the ear
 thly life of Jesus of Nazareth. We will examine the Christian scriptures\, 
 other religious antecedents\, the stories that became attached to Jesus aft
 er the fact\, and how to make sense of them in a Unitarian Universalist con
 text. Sources consulted will include the 4 Gospel stories\, the Hebrew scri
 ptures' tale of the Passover\, informed commentary\, as well as parallels i
 n world religions. Only $5! Bring your own Bible.\n\nRegister here:\n\nJoin
  with Google Meet: https://meet.google.com/yii-vbmx-vfr\nOr dial: (US) +1 5
 30-675-6199 PIN: 206069250#\n\nLearn more about Meet at: https://support.go
 ogle.com/a/users/answer/9282720
LAST-MODIFIED:20221206T042608Z
LOCATION:Peierls
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Spring Bible Study - A UU Lens on the End of Jesus' Life
