DTSTAMP:20260311T022957Z
UID:36g6dvrv2h2frr7gbstgvei90b@google.com
CREATED:20220616T161235Z
DESCRIPTION:<br><a href="https://onrealm.org/uumontclair/PublicRegistration
 s/Event?linkString=Yjc4M2E5ZmItYWI4YS00NWRjLTg2MWItYWViNjAxMGFjYWVj" id="ow
 2766" __is_owner="true">RSVP HERE</a><br><br>Come one\, come all to Rifle C
 amp Park on Sunday\,&nbsp\;<b>July 10\, 2022</b>&nbsp\;from 12:00 to 4:00 P
 M!&nbsp\;<br><br>All are welcome to join this laidback mid-summer gathering
  in a beautiful\, historic setting offering nature trails\, multiple playgr
 ounds\, and open-air for safe socializing.&nbsp\;This is a great opportunit
 y to come together and reunite with folks you haven’t seen in a while.<br><
 br>We will have lawn games like corn hole and bocce\, outdoor activities\, 
 and fun for all ages.&nbsp\;There will be hotdogs &amp\; veggie dogs fresh 
 from the grill\, as well as some snacks and drinks.&nbsp\;You are invited t
 o bring your own picnic foods to grill on the park grills\, snacks to munch
 \, and nonalcoholic beverages to sip (sharing is welcome\, but not required
 ).&nbsp\;Musical folks\, bring your instruments and hand percussion for imp
 romptu jam sessions and song circles.<br><br>We are all part of one big\, h
 appy family at the U\, so let’s gather like one!&nbsp\;
LAST-MODIFIED:20220616T161235Z
LOCATION:Rifle Camp Park\, 387 Rifle Camp Rd\, Woodland Park\, NJ 07424\, U
 SA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:UUCM's ReUUnion Picnic
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
