DTEND:20221004T010000Z
DTSTAMP:20260311T022957Z
UID:5rrsitlug69fl0c0rrg3bhpo1i@google.com
CREATED:20220919T143407Z
DESCRIPTION:<html-blob><u></u><p><a href="https://onrealm.org/uumontclair/P
 ublicRegistrations/Event?linkString=ODZhM2RjOWYtOTcyOC00YzliLTg0YjMtYWYxNTA
 xMWQ0M2M0" id="ow1077" __is_owner="true">REGISTER HERE</a></p><p>The Congre
 gational Focus Team of "Undoing Racism" is organizing a number of focus gro
 ups\, to explore our congregation's work on the eighth principle. We aim to
  hear diverse and representative voices from every corner of our congregati
 on.</p><p><br></p><p>&nbsp\;As a leader\, we invite you to sign up for one 
 of the first focus groups. We encourage all to share thoughts and opinions 
 in a confidential small group format. Content\, but no names\, will be reco
 rded for analysis\, in hopes of guiding us forward.</p><p><br></p><p>&nbsp\
 ;Please choose between a&nbsp\;<strong>virtual group on Monday\, Oct. 3 at 
 7:30 P.M</strong>. or an&nbsp\;<strong>in-person group</strong><strong>&nbs
 p\;at the U&nbsp\;</strong><strong>on Sunday\, October 30 at 11:15\, immedi
 ately following the service.</strong>.&nbsp\; Each group will run up to 90 
 minutes.</p><p><br></p><p>&nbsp\;Questions?&nbsp\; <a href="mailto:undoingr
 acism@uumontclair.org?subject=URT%20Focus%20Group">Please reach out to Laur
 en Carlton</a>\, Board member and member of the URT 8th&nbsp\;principle foc
 us workgroup.</p><u></u></html-blob>
LAST-MODIFIED:20220919T171910Z
LOCATION:Zoom Video Conference
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:URT Focus Group
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
