DESCRIPTION:<p><strong><b>The Chalice Choir</b></strong>&nbsp\;is open to a
 nyone who enjoys singing. No need to audition\, and reading music is not a 
 requirement. The choir sings a wide repertoire of music\, from Handel to Ni
 na Simone\, Leonard Cohen and Bobby McFerrin. Opportunities to solo or sing
  in small groups are often available for more confident singers.</p><p>Regu
 lar rehearsals are on<strong><b>&nbsp\;Wednesday evenings from 7:30 to 9:00
  PM</b></strong>&nbsp\;in the Sanctuary.<a href="mailto:musicdir@uumontclai
 r.org" id="ow2068" __is_owner="true"> For more information contact Markus.<
 /a>&nbsp\;</p>\n\nJoin with Google Meet: https://meet.google.com/cmc-cgur-o
 os\nOr dial: (US) +1 929-282-1034 PIN: 152997316#\nMore phone numbers: http
 s://tel.meet/cmc-cgur-oos?pin=1995287906654&hs=7\n\nLearn more about Meet a
 t: https://support.google.com/a/users/answer/9282720
