CREATED:20220613T195154Z
DESCRIPTION:<html-blob>Are you new to The U and interested in membership? W
 e are so glad you have found your way here! Join us for our Pathways to Mem
 bership class! Now is the time to consider deepening your understanding of 
 the Unitarian Universalist tradition and our congregational life. This clas
 s is your path to becoming a member of Unitarian Universalist Congregation 
 at Montclair. Bring your questions and your hopes. Building community takes
  intention. This is one important step on that intentional path.<br><br><a 
 href="https://onrealm.org/uumontclair/PublicRegistrations/Event?linkString=
 MzZlMzc4MjAtNzlkYy00M2Y2LTgwYjAtYWViMzAxNDcyYjNm" id="ow1498" __is_owner="t
 rue">Register Today!</a></html-blob>
LAST-MODIFIED:20220616T182928Z
LOCATION:Zoom Video Conference\, UUCM-1-Peierls (60) [Multiplatform]
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Pathways to Membership- Multiplatform 
TRANSP:OPAQUE
