UID:5n2jt8u9cf238bb438p0qn04sq@google.com
CREATED:20221115T143823Z
DESCRIPTION:<html-blob><u></u><u></u><p><a href="https://onrealm.org/uumont
 clair/PublicRegistrations/Event?linkString=ODZhM2RjOWYtOTcyOC00YzliLTg0YjMt
 YWYxNTAxMWQ0M2M0">REGISTER HERE</a></p><p>The Congregational Focus Team of 
 "Undoing Racism" is organizing a number of focus groups\, to explore our co
 ngregation's work on the eighth principle. We aim to hear diverse and repre
 sentative voices from every corner of our congregation.</p><p><br></p><p>&n
 bsp\;As a leader\, we invite you to sign up for one of the first focus grou
 ps. We encourage all to share thoughts and opinions in a confidential small
  group format. Content\, but no names\, will be recorded for analysis\, in 
 hopes of guiding us forward.</p><p><span style="background-color: var(--tex
 tfield-surface)\; color: var(--on-surface)\;">Please choose a date to atten
 d:</span><br></p><ul><li><strong></strong><strong>Zoom event on Monday Dece
 mber 5th at 7:30PM<br></strong></li><li><strong>In person&nbsp\; Sunday Dec
 ember 11th at 11:30 AM.</strong></li></ul><p>&nbsp\;Each group will run up 
 to 90 minutes.</p><p><br></p><p>&nbsp\;Questions?&nbsp\; <a href="mailto:un
 doingracism@uumontclair.org?subject=URT%20Focus%20Group">Please reach out t
 o Lauren Carlton</a>\, Board member and member of the URT 8th&nbsp\;princip
 le focus workgroup.</p><u></u><u></u></html-blob>
LAST-MODIFIED:20221115T143823Z
LOCATION:Zoom Video Conference\, UUCM-1-Mortenson (15) [Multiplatform]\, UU
 CM-1-Peierls (60) [Multiplatform]
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:URT Focus Group - Virtual
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
