DESCRIPTION:<html-blob>The holiday season is sometimes very challenging eve
 n without a pandemic. UUCM Sacred Wheel CUUPs is offering a grounding and c
 entering workshop to teach you how to stay grounded.&nbsp\;Grounding is a w
 ay of eliminating excess energy or negativity. Learn simple but valuable gr
 ounding and centering tools to help you get through these uncertain times. 
 Join us to learn these important techniques to keep balanced through the re
 st of 2022.&nbsp\; All are welcome&nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\;<a href="mailto:sacr
 edwheelcuups@uumontclair.org">For more information email Ann.&nbsp\;</a></h
 tml-blob>
LAST-MODIFIED:20221114T163500Z
LOCATION:Zoom Video Conference
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Sacred Wheel CUUPs Grounding and Centering Workshop
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
