DESCRIPTION:Harvesters!\n\nWe Reconvene this Thursday\, Nov 7\, at 730 PM i
 n the Peierls Room.The focus is on UUCM History. We will be led by Irene Sa
 nderson\, co-Chair of our Archives. Irene will share a presentation prepare
 d by her and her co-chair Becky Doggett.\n\nHomework: Read the document cal
 led "Church History" - it is about the history of UUCM. Come to class with 
 one burning question or observation.Plus - There will be a quiz with prizes
 !!\n\nHere is another version of our history created in 2016: https://www.u
 umontclair.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/UUCM-History-10-pages1-1.pdf\n\nI
  have also included the Workshop Materials for this session\, called "Our U
 nitarian Universalist Journey." We will not cover much of this in class\, a
 s we will give the lion's share of our time to the Archives presentation.\n
 \nLooking forward to gathering with you all again!\nThanks\nRev Scott\n\nJo
 in with Google Meet: https://meet.google.com/dyg-puhn-zge\nOr dial: (US) +1
  559-633-9077 PIN: 389120001#\n\nLearn more about Meet at: https://support.
 google.com/a/users/answer/9282720
LAST-MODIFIED:20221206T042820Z
LOCATION:Mortenson\, Peierls
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Harvest the Power - UU Journey
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
