DESCRIPTION:<html-blob><b>“Reading Scripture with Pride”</b><br><p><u></u><
 /p><p>On Tuesday\, June 7\, 7PM\, at the Unitarian Universalist Congregatio
 n at Montclair\, 67 Church Street\, a group of Interfaith Clergy and Laity 
 will present “Reading Scripture with Pride.” We will hear from LGBTQ people
  of faith on their experiences\, and clergy will each reflect on why Sacred
  Scriptures should not be weaponized against LGBTQ people. The event will b
 e live-streamed and a Reception will follow.</p><p><br></p><p>Reception - N
 ormal CC set up</p><p>Tea\, Water\, Lemonade and cookies</p><u></u></html-b
 lob>\n\nJoin with Google Meet: https://meet.google.com/ids-kess-dez\nOr dia
 l: (US) +1 847-957-1915 PIN: 989005514#\nMore phone numbers: https://tel.me
 et/ids-kess-dez?pin=1201067766341&hs=7\n\nLearn more about Meet at: https:/
 /support.google.com/a/users/answer/9282720
