CREATED:20220809T133919Z
DESCRIPTION:<html-blob><br>Dear UUCM Members\, Friends and Guests\,<br><br>
 It is with heavy heart that we write to inform you of the passing of Naja J
 ohn\, just 20 years old. Naja died this past Friday\, August 5\, 2022\, in 
 her apartment in Boston. Naja's parents\, Nina and Andre\, are comfortable 
 with folks reaching out to show support in this difficult time.<br><br>Naja
 \, who grew up attending UUCM\, and was a graduate of our Coming of Age pro
 gram\, will be dearly missed.<br><br>A Celebration of Life Service will be 
 held on Naja's behalf on<b>&nbsp\;Monday\, August 22\, 2022\, at 2:00 PM&nb
 sp\;</b>in the UUCM Sanctuary\, with a light repast to follow in Fletcher H
 all.<br><br><b>The service will also be live-streamed for those who wish to
  attend virtually</b>. Please&nbsp\;<a href="https://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=0
 01FPyLM1mRhh_RJJ18t0J2qpRl2eedFNO-_PFR8gT6O0lKo9Ea6l9dkIwTpG7fvyZQiWPpdy0N2
 1oES_7mKS-LmtQiwAJtq0DRTUwadJcvQjBUWJ9wdKaH4XkIO0DeYOFiHW_B-sfGVrO2oU4dBaqS
 n5rT6DnQKyJ2uj2uHMV0T28=&c=CGIIkSHHO5HvJSX4HV04ANPcGD2g3nrdf5RAc34jx1z57T2q
 _bZLlA==&ch=H50qWPDtxjWTf277O-25izYgmglFoU8m0WFr0ho66p5qY509u5PSng=="><b><u
 >click here</u></b></a>&nbsp\;to join the live-stream.<br><br>If you are ca
 lled to volunteer at the memorial service please contact Rev. Anya at&nbsp\
 ;<a href="mailto:revanya@uumontclair.org"><u>revanya@uumontclair.org</u></a
 >.<br><br>Your prayers of support and love are needed in this difficult tim
 e for Naja's family and all who know and love them.</html-blob>
LAST-MODIFIED:20220811T153341Z
LOCATION:UUCM-1-Sanctuary (265) [Multiplatform]\, UUCM-1-Fletcher Hall (306
 )\, UUCM-1-Alliance (10) [Multiplatform]\, UUCM-1-Kitchen (10)
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Celebration of Life for Naja John
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
