 th Group\, \nSunday\, January 27\, 5pm in Fletcher Hall. Come join us for a
 n evening of \ngames: board games\, kindergarten games\, card games\, camp 
 games\, all \nkinds of games\, except video games. Games will be led by UUC
 M Senior Youth. Pizza\, snacks\, and drinks will be served by Senior Youth 
  advisors/families. \n\n$5 for adults and youth. Free for children 6th grad
 e and below\, who MUST be accompanied by an adult. This event was offered a
 s an Auction Event. We are now opening it up to the whole congregation\, ev
 en if you didn't bid on it at the Auction. Please contact Kate Loysen  \nTu
 rek with questions\, kloysen@gmail.com
