DTEND:20171022T010000Z
DTSTAMP:20260311T022957Z
UID:5sqefch7eo122g09b4pnn63b3v@google.com
CREATED:20170912T190122Z
DESCRIPTION:Woven Green Soundscapes - A meditative journey through the powe
 r of sound\nBring a yoga mat\, pillow\, and blanket for an hour of bliss! (
 chairs also provided).\n\nSound healer\, singer-songwriter duo\, Woven Gree
 n provides a unique sound bath experience\, using sound as an intentionally
  activated energetic tool to elevate and realign meditators to a higher and
  more harmonious frequency. The couple seamlessly weaves the sounds of crys
 tal and Tibetan singing bowls\, native flutes and drums\, nature sounds\, v
 ocal toning\, wind gong\, and stringed instruments creating textures of soo
 thing melodies and harmonies and gentle rhythms that quickly envelop listen
 ers in a healing sonic field.\nWoven Green Soundscapes are designed to guid
 e listeners into theta brain wave states\, which are proven to help reduce 
 stress\, awaken intuition\, enhance creativity\, and promote an overall exp
 anded state of well- being.\n\nAudiences report profound transcendental exp
 eriences\, enhanced inner vision\, and stress relief. You won’t want to mis
 s it!\n\nWhen we align with the harmonious frequencies of nature and the hi
 gher vibratory states of unconditional love and bliss\, we become attuned t
 o an energetic potential that can transform and bring balance to both our i
 nner and outer worlds.\n\nCONCERT - A Mystical Evening with Woven Green\nA 
 Tale of transformation Weaving songs\, healing sounds\, and storytelling\n\
 nJoin Woven Green for an intimate\, soulful\, and unique concert experience
 . This dynamic husband-wife duo\, blend their original contemporary folk\, 
 rock\, world\, and new age music in a spiritual stream of consciousness tha
 t invites listeners to the transcendental and mythic world they so passiona
 tely inhabit. Watch and listen as the couple synergistically flows between 
 instru- ments (including guitars\, native flutes\, keys\, loop stations\, a
 nd other world instruments)\, story- telling\, and relevant\, potent lyrica
 l content from songs off their debut award-winning album\, “Into Bloom.”\n\
 nNoteworthy music review says\, “Woven Green's album\, 'Into Bloom\,' is a 
 standout work of inspi- ration art that reflects the undeniable musicianshi
 p and vocal talent of this one of a kind group. From ballads\, to rocking j
 ams and native inspired tunes\, Woven Green is an extremely versatile group
  that offers listeners a journey into something that is even deeper than th
 e music itself – a connection\, a healing\, a growing\, a spiritual experie
 nce and a chance to see nature through the eyes\, hearts and voices of the 
 duo.”\n
LAST-MODIFIED:20221206T044235Z
LOCATION:Fletcher Hall\, Sanctuary\, Kitchen
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Woven Green Sound Bath and Concert
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
