UID:ldfc8ko3p4f8sp4uf1scb7tsu4@google.com
CREATED:20220920T144854Z
DESCRIPTION:Hello lucky winners of my "Raising the Roof! Family Drum Circle
 " from this year's Benevolent Bash!<br><br>We will start promptly at 10:30a
 m Saturday&nbsp\;Sept 24\, in the UUCM Sanctuary\; we will go until about&n
 bsp\;noon.<br><br>If you have a drum\, please bring it! Let me know if you 
 have one you&nbsp\;are&nbsp\;bringing.<br>I will have many percussion&nbsp\
 ;instruments\, but I may not have enough drums to have one for everyone (al
 though I will have other things for you to&nbsp\;play\, and we will share a
 nd swap instruments often throughout our time together).&nbsp\;<br><br>We w
 ill explore the nature of rhythm in general\, focusing on the rhythms all a
 round us\; I will share some hand-drumming techniques\; we will work on pla
 ying all manner of percussion instruments\; and then we will have some drum
  circles\, and even compose a piece together!<br><br><b>BONUS:&nbsp\;</b>An
 d anyone who wants to stick around until 1pm\, we can 'Drum In' the teacher
 s as they begin the teacher orientation for our&nbsp\;Children's Program.<b
 r><br>Yours in faith and music\,<br>Rev Scott
LAST-MODIFIED:20220920T144911Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Family Drum Circle - in Sanctuary
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
