DESCRIPTION:<html-blob><u></u><a href="https://tinyurl.com/SpringConnect202
 2">REGISTER HERE</a><u></u><br><p>We hope you have been enjoying getting to
  know the Unitarian Universalist Congregation at Montclair. Now that the we
 ather is warming\, we would like to invite you to join us for a special Con
 nection Cafe especially for New Members and Newcomers. This is a great way 
 to meet and get to know more of our Congregation’s members and those who ar
 e beginning their journeys\, like you.</p><p><br></p><p>Date: Sunday\, May 
 15</p><p>Time: 11:00 or immediately after services</p><p>Where: Outside on 
 the lawn by the front entrances. If it rains\, we will move into Fletcher H
 all.</p><p><br></p><p>Light refreshments will be served. As we will be outs
 ide\, masks are optional but please do what you feel is best for you. If yo
 u already have your nametag\, please bring it with you. If not\, one will b
 e provided for you.</p><p><strong><b>We hope to see you soon\, finally in p
 erson!</b></strong></p><br><u></u><u></u><u></u></html-blob>
LAST-MODIFIED:20220609T153115Z
LOCATION:UUCM-1-Fletcher Hall (306)
SEQUENCE:8
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Themed Connection Cafe- New Member Celebration
TRANSP:OPAQUE
