 n the deck or porch at the home of Marcia Mandel and Elaine Gibson. All are
  welcome!&nbsp\;<br><br>This will be a pot-luck event\; bring something to 
 share (maybe a Jewish-style food or nosh that you remember from childhood?)
 . And please RSVP to&nbsp\;<a href="mailto:jewishawareness@uumontclair.org"
  id="ow858" __is_owner="true">jewishawareness@uumontclair.<wbr>org</a>.
