 gin with a worship experience created just for you\, the faithful UU leader
 . What kind of community are we creating in this time when everything and e
 veryone is new again - forged new out of collective trauma\, out of societa
 l shifting\, out of emerging needs and hopes for our world. We can find new
  ground together in ways that you can bring back to your people. Please joi
 n us. Led by Central East Region staff.</p><p>Connection Information:</p><p
 >Join Zoom Meeting</p><p><a href="https://uua.zoom.us/j/99600842058?pwd=cEt
