DESCRIPTION:<br>For those unfamiliar -healing circles are similar to prayer
 s. Healing could be for physical\, emotional or spiritual. It is the intent
  we put into it. If you would like to assist or have a request for yourself
  or someone else\, please join us. If you like to join in and have no exper
 ience\, we will teach you. Alternatively\, if you are new to this\, you can
  just sit back and observe. Stick around afterwards for a sharing of ghost 
 stories. All are welcome.<br><br>Join Zoom Meeting<br><a href="https://us06
 web.zoom.us/j/85619922755?pwd=WXRNVlVSektvNzdkZmZ5bjdscjNLZz09"><u>https://
