 UCMPTM0124</a><br><br><u></u><u></u>Are you new to The U and interested in 
 membership? We are so glad you have found your way here! Join us for our Pa
 thways to Membership class! Now is the time to consider deepening your unde
 rstanding of the Unitarian Universalist tradition and our congregational li
 fe. This class is your path to becoming a member of Unitarian Universalist 
 Congregation at Montclair. Bring your questions and your hopes. Building co
 mmunity takes intention. This is one important step on that intentional pat
 h.<br><br><a href="https://onrealm.org/uumontclair/PublicRegistrations/Even
 t?linkString=NmZlYzY2NmItNmVkOC00OGE5LWE2ZWEtYjBhMDAwZTBmZDY5">Register Tod
 ay!</a><u></u><u></u>
