DESCRIPTION:<u></u><br>The Winter Solstice is the shortest day of the year.
  We know today that the Sun will return\, because of the course of the Sun 
 and through scientific exploration of other planets in our solar system. Ou
 r ancestors did not take the return of the Sun for granted\, and in additio
 n\, they were suffering much more under the hardships of severe winter weat
 her than we do today. Join us as we welcome the return of the Sun.. All are
  welcome.<br> For more info on Sacred Wheel\, email <a href="mailto:sacredw
 heel@uumontclair.org">sacredwheel@uumontclair.org</a>.<u></u>
LAST-MODIFIED:20231122T184148Z
LOCATION:UUCM-1-Alliance (10) [Multiplatform]
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Sacred Wheel CUUPs Winter Solstice Ritual
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
