DESCRIPTION:We will gather with all ages and all species on the front lawn 
 of our Congregation\n\nWith joy\, song and ritual we will bless our pets\, 
 and our dear stuffed animals. \n\nThis service draws from the inspiration o
 f St. Francis of Assisi. In this Unitarian Universalist version we will tak
 e a moment to grieve the animals that have died\, share our gratitude for t
 he animals that make our lives better\, bless the animals that make their h
 ome among us\, and commit to treating our animals like partners not things.
 \n\nPlease bring donations of pet food\, treats\, used towels\, or monetary
  contributions to serve animals in local shelters.
LAST-MODIFIED:20230802T140338Z
LOCATION:UUCM-1-Front Lawn (100)
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Animal Blessing
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
