UID:4qn55utf0k61oib9ltqh9puqre@google.com
CREATED:20240224T125338Z
DESCRIPTION:Live in our Sanctuary<br>And Live Streamed: <a href="https://ww
 w.facebook.com/uumontclair/live_videos/?__cft__[0]=AZXy1SchMdQ3QSMrzR8kPE93
 lf0P22fFUfgUeNb0vQL9VYMT8wIIRpX7ocUnFPRiIycq7b880PP1GbfLjdLiQlHm2iJSMrKsJac
 PndyypdQPl8RtiOEK7fEvb8Pty9IemWszaEOXPKU7O1PX3yhiQkRlqjVnyNCR0sMNRap7Ta0bRg
 &amp\;__tn__=R]-R">https://www.facebook.com/uumontclair/live_videos/</a><br
 ><span><br></span><br><span>We come together on Sunday to grieve the loss o
 f this beautiful soul. As our hearts break\, we stand in solidarity with op
 en hearts to carry forward the spirit of Nex's shining light. Let their lif
 e move us towards justice for other young folxs who are bullied and continu
 e to suffer from anti-trans policies. Please join us Sunday\, Feb 25th at 1
 :00 at UUCM for a Vigil to honor and remember the life of Nex Benedict. Nex
  Benedict was a non-binary\, 16 year student from Oklahoma\, who was bullie
 d and beaten at school on Feb 7th and passed away on Feb 8th. Let's show up
  to share our love and support for our trans\, non-binary and genderfluid f
 riends and family.</span>
LAST-MODIFIED:20240224T125338Z
LOCATION:Unitarian Universalist Congregation at Montclair
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Vigil for Nex Benedict
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
