DESCRIPTION:<br><b>Newcomer Connections - First Sundays from&nbsp\;<span>12
 :45-1:15pm</span>&nbsp\;in the Alliance Room</b><br><ul><li>New to the Unit
 arian Universalist Congregation at Montclair?&nbsp\;</li><li>Visiting or "C
 ongregation Shopping" for yourself or your family?&nbsp\;</li><li>Want to k
 now a bit more about our congregation and the Unitarian Universalist tradit
 ion?</li></ul>Join with one of our ministers and other newcomers to for a s
 hort\, honest\, in-depth conversation. All of your questions will be honore
 d. Child care is available. Children age 12 and above are welcome to partic
 ipate. A bagel brunch will be provided. RSVP with our&nbsp\;<a href="mailto
 :admin@uumontclair.org" target="_blank">Administrator</a>.&nbsp\;<br><br>Se
 tup: Coffee and hot water setup
