DESCRIPTION:<p>The UUCM Senior Lunch Bunch" was formed in 1999 to provide a
  friendly place for UUCM members and their friends to meet\; to get acquain
 ted with one another and their friends\; to share their interests\, concern
 s\, and happenings\; and generally to be friends. [NOTE: People of all ages
  are welcome to join our group. We define a "senior person" as one who know
 s who they are and has ideas and questions about what is going on around us
 .] We meet on the 2nd and 4th Wednesdays at 12 noon until 1:30 PM to share 
 important happenings in our lives and our ideas\, opinions\, and questions 
 about subjects of interest to members of the group.<br></p><p><u><a href="m
 ailto:admin@uumontclair.org">Email for more information</a></u></p><p><br><
 /p><p>Join Zoom Meeting<br><a href="https://us06web.zoom.us/j/92827563951?p
 wd=YTJNQ2dreVZQUktDTzd4YnRMQWVhZz09"><u>https://us06web.zoom.us/j/928275639
 51?pwd=YTJNQ2dreVZQUktDTzd4YnRMQWVhZz09</u></a><br>Meeting ID: 928 2756 395
 1<br>Passcode: UUCM<br></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20240112T153500Z
