DESCRIPTION:<p dir="ltr">Save the Date! Please join us\, and spread the wor
 d to fellow leaders and friends: on May 24th at 7pm as we officially launch
  our Essex County chapter of New Jersey Together at Bethany Baptist Church\
 , 275 West Market Street\, Newark. Essex Together will join our existing ch
 apters\, Jersey City Together and Morris Area Together\, to help multiply a
 nd build the power necessary to address local and statewide issues such as 
 criminal justice reform\, clean energy\, affordable housing\, and more. To 
 make this launch as impactful as possible\, we need to have at least 250 pe
 ople there. Towards that end\, we hope each organization involved in New Je
 rsey Together - Essex\, will commit to bring at least 7 to 10 people with t
 hem (and more if you can!). </p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20230523T145030Z
LOCATION:Bethany Baptist Church\, 275 West Market Street\, Newark\, NJ 0710
 2
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Essex Launch
TRANSP:OPAQUE
