CREATED:20240611T143618Z
DESCRIPTION:<br>Below is a list of possible resources and organizations we 
 can consider using to help us in this work and possible trainings for justi
 ce leaders. By all means this is not a comprehensive list\, just what I hav
 e found so far and what a few other people have suggested. If you have any 
 additional resources please feel free to share them.  Before our meeting\, 
 it would be helpful for everyone to take a look at them so we have a place 
 to start the conversation.<br>Two articles I shared with SJCT - just to giv
 e a sense of how deep listening can be used in social justice and social ch
 ange work<br><br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://corinejansen
 .com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Winter-2022-Feature-Kasriel-Listening-1.pdf
 &amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;ust=1718137214725513&amp\;usg=AOvVaw2M
 OV76OhvgkII6WoSHAI4T" target="_blank">Deep Listening Stanford Social Innova
 tion Review </a><br><br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://great
 ergood.berkeley.edu/article/item/can_deep_listening_heal_our_divisions?utm_
 campaign%3Deb54851831-EMAIL_CAMPAIGN_GG_Newsletter_January_26_2021%26utm_me
 dium%3Demail%26utm_source%3DGreater%2520Good%2520Science%2520Center%26utm_t
 erm%3D0_5ae73e326e-eb54851831-52074031&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;
 ust=1718137214725513&amp\;usg=AOvVaw2db_fnh6i_M3OfwkGsSqOS" target="_blank"
 >Bridging The Gap - Can Deep Listening Heal our Divisions</a><br><br><u>Lis
 t of Organizations/Resources</u><br><p dir="ltr">1. Courageous Conversation
 s - Glen Singleton </p><p dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=h
 ttps://courageousconversation.com/&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;ust=
 1718137214725513&amp\;usg=AOvVaw0JFKZNXHaNo1LpqPNeQJl9" target="_blank">htt
 ps://<u></u>courageousconversation.com</a></p><p dir="ltr">2. Interfaith Am
 erica  - Bridgebuilding curriculum </p><p dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.go
 ogle.com/url?q=https://www.interfaithamerica.org/curricula/btg-curriculum/&
 amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;ust=1718137214725513&amp\;usg=AOvVaw1wj
 HfHG2dNHMmg1yY8Ijwh" target="_blank">https://www.interfaithamerica.<u></u>o
 rg/curricula/btg-curriculum/</a><br></p><p>3. Social Movements Innovation</
 p><p dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://socialmovement
 sinnovation.org/tools/deep-listening/%23section-tools&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source
 =calendar&amp\;ust=1718137214725513&amp\;usg=AOvVaw0JbRbK9LTjaAqMDI0zIi7v" 
 target="_blank"><u>https://<u></u>socialmovementsinnovation.org/<u></u>tool
 s/deep-listening/#section-<u></u>tools</u></a></p><p>4. Just Listening</p><
 p dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://justlistening.net
 /services/training/&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;ust=171813721472551
 3&amp\;usg=AOvVaw1x-yjTJbSvilW3eMC99V0C" target="_blank"><u>https://justlis
 tening.net/<u></u>services/training/</u></a></p><p dir="ltr"><a href="https
 ://www.google.com/url?q=https://justlistening.net/the-little-book-of-just-l
 istening/&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;ust=1718137214725513&amp\;usg
 =AOvVaw2XFTu5f_M6dI8t-fBA7WDa" target="_blank">https://justlistening.net/th
 e-<u></u>little-book-of-just-listening/</a><br></p><p>5.The Learning Collab
 orative</p><p dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://thele
 arningcollaborative.com/deep-listening/&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\
 ;ust=1718137214725513&amp\;usg=AOvVaw2py9eLJI-MFqjtVqXfe6bM" target="_blank
 "><u>https://<u></u>thelearningcollaborative.com/<u></u>deep-listening/</u>
 </a></p><p>6.Deep Canvassing</p><p dir="ltr"><u><a href="https://www.google
 .com/url?q=https://commonslibrary.org/deep-canvassing-to-shift-hearts-mind-
 and-votes/&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;ust=1718137214725513&amp\;us
 g=AOvVaw3XpyNAKE-hzhyXni3nFn--" target="_blank">https://commonslibrary.org/
 <u></u>deep-canvassing-to-shift-<u></u>hearts-mind-and-votes/</a></u></p><p
  dir="ltr">7. Braver Angels - UUCM Electoral Justice and LWV co-sponsored a
  talk from Braver Angels a few weeks ago that was well attended and receive
 d positive feedback<br></p><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://br
 averangels.org/&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;ust=1718137214725513&am
 p\;usg=AOvVaw37x6DsPucg6eLZrIDmbzyz" target="_blank">https://braverangels.o
 rg/</a><br>8. Non-violent communication - Marshall Rosenberg<br><a href="ht
 tps://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.cnvc.org/about&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source
 =calendar&amp\;ust=1718137214725513&amp\;usg=AOvVaw3ksr0D1ixPvbMsJcvTHZDJ" 
 target="_blank">https://www.cnvc.org/about</a><br>9. <a href="https://www.g
 oogle.com/url?q=https://www.changeimpact.net/&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calenda
 r&amp\;ust=1718137214725513&amp\;usg=AOvVaw0WMelEp2yL_JKkYP8WljQw" target="
 _blank">https://www.changeimpact.<u></u>net/</a><br>10. <a href="https://ww
 w.google.com/url?q=https://changeuplearning.com/&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=cale
 ndar&amp\;ust=1718137214725513&amp\;usg=AOvVaw0zhVFihbT3Wt-D927JIAhh" targe
 t="_blank">https://changeuplearning.<u></u>com/</a><br><br>Best\, Maria\n\n
 Join with Google Meet: https://meet.google.com/gmq-trwx-egi\nOr dial: (US) 
 +1 337-346-2830 PIN: 610356004#\nMore phone numbers: https://tel.meet/gmq-t
 rwx-egi?pin=1798900397795&hs=7\n\nLearn more about Meet at: https://support
 .google.com/a/users/answer/9282720
LAST-MODIFIED:20240612T023301Z
LOCATION:UUCM-1-Peierls (60) [Multiplatform]
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:SJCT Convo on Deep Listening
TRANSP:OPAQUE
