CREATED:20160707T152331Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Be it a queen-sized bed quilt or decorator pillows\, the wor
 k done by the&nbsp\;<strong>Crazy QUUilters</strong>&nbsp\;brings joy to th
 e creators and the recipients. Among our current projects are lap quilts lo
 vingly made for UUCM members as a warm reminder of our congregation’s thoug
 hts and prayers.</p><p>In normal times\, the Crazy QUUilters&nbsp\;meet in 
 the Rotunda on the third Saturday of each month. During this challenging ti
 me we continue to stay connected through&nbsp\;<strong>ZOOM on the third Sa
 turday at 11:00 AM</strong>. &nbsp\;An email will be sent to our membership
  with ZOOM meeting information. &nbsp\;The work done by the Crazy QUUilters
  brings joy to the creators and the recipients. Among our current projects 
 are lap quilts lovingly made for UUCM members as a warm reminder of our con
 gregation’s thoughts and prayers. We have also decided to offer the compani
 onship of our monthly meetings to other crafters.&nbsp\; If you knit\, croc
 het or do other hand work you are welcome to join us for about 4 hours of s
 hared creating. The workshop is open to all willing hands (previous experie
 nce not required).</p><p><br></p><p><a href="mailto:crazyquilters@uumontcla
 ir.org" id="ow7845" __is_owner="true">For more information contact Arlene</
 a></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20240409T150733Z
LOCATION:Zoom Video Conference
SEQUENCE:2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Crazy QUUilters 
TRANSP:OPAQUE
