DESCRIPTION:<p>All are welcome to join the annual interfaith Yom HaShoah Ho
 locaust commemoration\, hosted by the Montclair Interfaith Clergy Associati
 on.</p><p><span>As part of the service\, we will hear from “third-generatio
 n survivors”. These grandchildren of Holocaust survivors did not witness th
 e same horrors of their grandparents\, but they bear witness to the pain\, 
 loss\, and physical and emotional scars. They will share what they have hea
 rd and witnessed of the harrowing journeys\, devastating loss and inspiring
  resilience of their grandparents.</span></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250403T151943Z
LOCATION:UUCM-1-Sanctuary (265) [Multiplatform]
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Yom HaShoah Interfaith Remembrance Service
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
