UID:3m72dluefsnec6m74pm192ddl7@google.com
CREATED:20250522T154812Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Register: <a href="https://tinyurl.com/UUCMTOT25">https://ti
 nyurl.com/UUCMTOT25</a></p><p>Join Rev Scott on the following Wednesdays: A
 ugust 6\, 13\, 20\, 27\, 2025\, 6-8pm for Theology on Tap - where we engage
  in public theology in a pub setting!</p><p>We will gather at 6pm\, get set
 tled in our space\, and have discussions on faith development\, theology\, 
 and contemporary society. This is a ’Covenant Group" style sharing\, but in
  a Pub setting. Drop-ins welcome! (The consumption of alcohol is not requir
 ed for this program). This is a "drop-in" program\, so come to one\, or com
 e to all!</p><p>Theology is as much a way to look at the world as it is a f
 ield of study. We are all natural born theologians\, but sadly not enough o
 f us get the training needed to tone our theological muscles. Come - develo
 p your theological chops in a fun setting!</p><p>This is open to all. Donat
 ions of $10 are accepted to defray renting the room. Participants are respo
 nsible for purchasing their own food and drink.</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250814T023337Z
LOCATION:Tierney's Tavern\, 138 Valley Rd\, Montclair\, NJ 07042\, USA
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Theology on Tap
TRANSP:OPAQUE
