DESCRIPTION:Join Rev Scott and DRE Judith Hogan Wednesday\, April 9 from 63
 0-830.\nIn the spirit of Deep Listening\, Rev Scott and DRE Judith invite t
 he stakeholders of our programming for children to come share with us your 
 hopes and ideas about our ministries to children and their families for the
  next congregational year.\nWe will make ourselves available to hear people
 ’s praise for our program and ideas of how to make it better.\nWe will also
  ask folks what kind of summer programming they want the staff to be involv
 ed in.\nThis event is in the Peierls Room\, and is Multiplatform.\n\nTopic:
  Listening Booth RE Session \nTime: Apr 9\, 2025 06:30 PM Eastern Time (US 
