CREATED:20250530T135846Z
DESCRIPTION:Arta Lucescu-Boutcher - 201 820-7477\n\nSunday\, June 29th at 1
 1:30 for my book presentation. I have written a memoir dedicated to my moth
 er. It presents our journey from Romania to New York and passing through Pa
 ris\; also our struggles as it was difficult to leave Romania in the 1970's
  and how we adjusted to living in the United States. Many pictures of artwo
 rk\, my own and those of my mother's\, are included (paintings\, pyro engra
 vings\, and tapestries.) My book is entitled "Loss\, Voyage\, and Rebirth" 
 and is available in print and as an ebook on Amazon. I plan to provide chee
 se\, crackers and wine.
LAST-MODIFIED:20250612T160114Z
LOCATION:UUCM-1-Alliance (10) [Multiplatform]
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Arta Boutcher Book Presentation
TRANSP:OPAQUE
