  a draw. Fletcher Hall for Silent Auction\n$40k\n\nFinalizing a date - Nove
 mber 22\nOnline goes live the 14\nMaximum of 10 Baskets?\nCan we stage them
  here the week before? Rotunda & …\nRestaurant gift certificates\n\n    Lis
 t of preferred features \n“Pajama Party”\n\nLessons learned from last year 
 about Planning\, Teams and Roll Out (as opposed to "night of event' details
 " - that's for another time) -  i.e. - we learned we should Open bidding on
  'stuff' one week before the event ...\nHybrid Bidding?\nNo single bidder c
 an win more than 2. \nUnderwriters\nUUCM Stock\n\nTeams - \nTech & catalogu
 e\,\nCheck in greeters\nbaskets and set up\, \nfood & beverages\, \ndecorat
 ions\, \nChid care\nMarketing\nRunners & counters\nlive auction team\, \nCh
 eck out\nClean up and\nReminders\n\nTeam makeup\, \nroles and leaders for e
 ach role.  \nWITT Tix \nRev Scott Sammler-Michael (he\, him\, his) is invit
