DESCRIPTION:<p>Are you interested in exploring the monthly themes through w
 riting and sharing with others? The purpose of this group is to write about
  the monthly theme before the meeting and share your writing with the group
 . Facilitated by Dennis Kurtti\, it will be held each month on the fourth S
 aturday. This is not a writing critique group\, and all levels of writing e
 xperience are welcome. If you would like to understand more about this kind
  of covenant group\, you can <a href="https://www.facebook.com/watch/live/?
 ref=watch_permalink&v=385146056918019" target="_blank">watch the worship se
 rvice</a> held on 8/21/22\, which featured speakers from an already existin
 g group. To express your interest in this group\, contact Laura Wilson at <
 a href="mailto:CovenantGroups@uumontclair.org" target="_blank">CovenantGrou
 ps@uumontclair.<u></u>org</a> </p><p>Join on Zoom: <a href="https://us06web
 .zoom.us/j/87640819050?pwd=WkRpeDM3bm1aVTlDRWY3Y3o3cFF3dz09" target="_blank
 "><u>https://us06web.zoom.us/j/87640819050?pwd=WkRpeDM3bm1aVTlDRWY3Y3o3cFF3
 dz09</u></a><br>Meeting ID: 876 4081 9050<br>Passcode: UUCM<br></p>
