DESCRIPTION:Register: <a href="https://tinyurl.com/UUCMDLSCI24">https://tin
 yurl.com/UUCMDLSCI24</a><br><p>UUCM is offering a supportive\, non-judgment
 al space for individuals of all gender identities who are childfree\, child
 less\, or unsure about having children to share their thoughts\, feelings\,
  and experiences. This session aims to foster deep listening and connection
 \, providing a compassionate environment for exploring this important\, per
 sonal decision.</p><b>Time</b>: Sunday\, 12/15 at Noon.<br><br><b>Other Inf
 o: </b>Please feel welcome to bring a brown bag lunch.<br>Questions? Please
  be in touch with Rev. Anya at <a href="mailto:revanya@uumontclair.org" tar
 get="_blank">revanya@uumontclair.org</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20241126T164903Z
LOCATION:UUCM-1-Alliance (10) [Multiplatform]
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Deep Listening Session for Our Community who Identifies as Childfre
 e\, Childless\, or Uncertain About Having Children
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
