 ngregation in ways that will sustain us as individual participants and supp
 ort our growth as a community. So grab your coffee and join us for a fun wa
 y to connect on Sunday morning. All are welcome. We hope you can join us!&n
 bsp\;<br><br><br><u></u></html-blob>
