DESCRIPTION:Register: <a href="https://tinyurl.com/UUCMAB25">https://tinyur
 l.com/UUCMAB25</a><br><br>We will gather with all ages and all species on t
 he front lawn of our Congregation<br><br>With joy\, song and ritual we will
  bless our pets\, and our dear stuffed animals. <br><br>This service draws 
 from the inspiration of St. Francis of Assisi. In this Unitarian Universali
 st version we will take a moment to grieve the animals that have died\, sha
 re our gratitude for the animals that make our lives better\, bless the ani
 mals that make their home among us\, and commit to treating our animals lik
 e partners not things.<br><br>Please bring donations of pet food\, treats\,
  used towels\, or monetary contributions to serve animals in local shelters
 .
