 ions about what is going on around us.] We meet on the 2nd and 4th Wednesda
 ys at 12 noon until 1:30 PM to share important happenings in our lives and 
 our ideas\, opinions\, and questions about subjects of interest to members 
 of the group. If you are not already a member of The UUCM Senior Lunch Bunc
 h\, we look forward to meeting you at one of our meetings in the near futur
