UID:05i4q9kparuvr3dd03fcnjpivn@google.com
CREATED:20260125T141605Z
DESCRIPTION:<br><p><strong>THE UUCM BUILDING IS CLOSED TODAY\, TOMORROW\, a
 nd maybe longer. </strong></p><p><strong>However\, Sunday service is ON! On
 line\, that is - and it can be found here: </strong><a href="https://youtu.
 be/w1iA7ZIORYk"><u>https://youtu.be/w1iA7ZIORYk</u></a><strong><em><br></em
 ></strong></p><figure></figure><p><strong><em>Keeping the Faith:Truth as Re
 sistance</em></strong>.  "Many of the problems of our society stem from bad
  theology\, from wrongheaded notions of what sacred scriptures say. By revi
 ewing the Scopes Trial of 1925\, we can see how these bad ideas have made o
 ur culture suffer before - from Biblical Literalism to notions that only a 
 select group of people should rule\, to conflating religion with ambition\,
  greed and politics.  We should be humble when interpreting scripture\, or 
 making claims about what God is or is not. It is stunning how some of the s
 ame ideas they debated in 1925 sound like they could be in today's newsfeed
 . Join us for an eye-opening walk through a Century old trial whose issues 
 remain relevant to our culture today."<br></p><p><strong>Thanks for your pa
 tience (for all the messages about this service)! </strong>We haven't done 
 a pre-recorded a service to premier since Covid - the last time was back in
  2021! Some of the tech has changed ... The Youtube link is above. Our tech
 s will also try to get it on Facebook for those who may prefer that platfor
 m.</p><p><strong>SPECIAL GIFTS FOR THIS SNOWY DAY! We have attached a Full 
 Script for those who like to read along (will not be verbatim\, of course!)
 . </strong></p><p><strong>We also have a special treat - 1923's <em><u>The 
 Battle Over the Bible</u> -</em>a pdf book version of one of the debates<em
 ><em> </em></em>between two NYC ministers - the fiery-tongued<em><em> </em>
 </em>Fundamentalist from Calvary Baptist\, John Roach Straton - and Charles
  Francis Potter\, Unitarian Minister serving at what is now called Fourth U
 niversalist Church\, on Central Park West. Potter preached at UUCM during h
 is career\, was a founder of the Humanist manifesto\, and offered theologic
 al analysis for the Scopes Trial of 1925.</strong></p><p><em><strong>Coming
  of Age is the only Children's program running today.</strong></em></p><p>P
 arent Support group is still on\, after services starting\, at 11:15\, virt
 ually - <br>Jan 25\, 2026 11:15 AM <strong><br>Register in advance for this
  meeting:</strong><br><a href="https://prodoula.zoom.us/meeting/register/Uu
 a67-lMS5WvzlDvW3fsmg"><u>https://prodoula.zoom.us/meeting/register/Uua67-lM
 S5WvzlDvW3fsmg</u></a><br>After registering\, you will receive a confirmati
 on email containing information about joining the meeting.</p><p>Any other 
 programs running\, please put them in the reply to this message.</p><p>Have
  a great Sunday! We will miss seeing you in person\, but we will see ya onl
 ine at 10AM.</p><br>Please join us in-person in our Sanctuary or <a href="h
 ttps://www.youtube.com/channel/UCiu_muZvGUZpyiDUfT88hMg" target="_blank"><u
 ><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u
 ><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u
 ><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u
 ><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>watch the live-stream online</u></u></u><
 /u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u>
 </u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u
 ></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></
 u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u><
 /u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a>.<br>Rev. Scott Sammler-Michael
