  with one another and their friends\; to share their interests\, concerns\,
  and happenings\; and generally to be friends. [NOTE: People of all ages ar
 e welcome to join our group. We define a "senior person" as one who knows w
 ho they are and has ideas and questions about what is going on around us.] 
