DESCRIPTION:The UUCM Senior Lunch Bunch" was formed in 1999 to provide a fr
 iendly place for UUCM members and their friends to meet\; to get acquainted
  with one another and their friends\; to share their interests\, concerns\,
  and happenings\; and generally to be friends. [NOTE: People of all ages ar
 e welcome to join our group. We define a "senior person" as one who knows w
 ho they are and has ideas and questions about what is going on around us.] 
 We meet on the 2nd and 4th Wednesdays at 12 noon until 1:30 PM to share imp
 ortant happenings in our lives and our ideas\, opinions\, and questions abo
 ut subjects of interest to members of the group. If you are not already a m
 ember of The UUCM Senior Lunch Bunch\, we look forward to meeting you at on
 e of our meetings in the near future.<br><p><u><a href="mailto:admin@uumont
 clair.org">Email for more information</a></u></p><p>Join Zoom Meeting<br><a
  href="https://us06web.zoom.us/j/92827563951?pwd=YTJNQ2dreVZQUktDTzd4YnRMQW
 VhZz09">https://us06web.zoom.us/j/92827563951?pwd=YTJNQ2dreVZQUktDTzd4YnRMQ
 WVhZz09</a><br>Meeting ID: 928 2756 3951<br>Passcode: UUCM<br></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260211T175908Z
LOCATION:Zoom Video Conference
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Senior Lunch Bunch 
TRANSP:OPAQUE
