DESCRIPTION:Our ANNUAL GARDEN PARTY in Jenny Sanderson Bakshi's Garden at 9
 1 South Mountain Ave. in Montclair\, NJ\, will take place on Wednesday\, Ju
 ne 19th. We will gather at 12 Noon and start by eating our lunches (<b><u>N
 ote:</u> </b>Bring your own lunch to eat on tables provided in Jenny's Gard
 en under the shade of the trees all around. Treats to share are always welc
 ome. Water will be available for drinking. <br><br>PARKING: Jenny's House a
 nd GARDEN is a short walk straight down the hill from the street. Please PA
 RK on South Mountain Ave. above Jenny's Garden. Parking on the street is le
 gal and necessary because parking at Jenny's house is extremely limited.<br
 ><br>COMFORT STATION: A toilet facility will be available.<br><br>QUESTIONS
 : Contact me if you have any questions. We have always had a good time at t
 hese ANNUAL GARDEN PARTIES\, and I am confident that this happy Result will
  be repeated this year.<br><br>Gary W. Sanderson (973-619-5556)
